snippet.title: Dead Cells: Fatal Falls - Official Animated Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the new, action-packed animated trailer for Dead Cells' latest DLC, Fatal Falls, which is available now.

The latest chapter in the animated trailer series introduces a clingy wannabe friend whose only wish is to hang out with Beheaded.

#DeadCells #IGN
